==English==
===Noun===
'''electronic game'''
# A [[game]] played on an [[electronic]] device.

===Usage Notes===
The term '''electronic game''' is the [[hypernym]] of the terms '''computer game''', '''video game''' and '''mobile game'''.  The term '''video game''' is historically restricted to games played on game consoles.  The term '''computer game''' is used to refer to electronic games played on a general purpose computer, especially an IBM-compatible personal computer or Apple Macintosh system.

